column5: 'ມີຜົນໄດ້ຮັບຂອງຄົນເຈັບນໍາໃຊ້?'

column3: 'Why was the patient not tested for malaria?'
column5: 'ມ່ນຄົນເຈັບຂອງທ່າ?'
'ຜູ້ຊາຍຫຼືແມ່ຍິງ?'

column3: 'What type of malaria does your patient have?'
'What type of treatment did you provide?'

column5: 'ນີ້ແມ່ນຄົນເຈັບເປັນຫຍັງ'

column3: 'Has the patient slept overnight outside of the village in the past two weeks?'
